Text.Value: I know a way, yes. Soon, you will be in the Absolute's presence.
She told me to decide your fate, to determine if you are worthy. If you are, I am to send you into Her embrace, at the seat of her power.

EditorData.NodeContext: genuine awe of the religious experience

Text.Value: If She wanted you dead, I would not spare you. You live by Her grace.
I believed for a moment that we might share a path. But I still sense that absence inside you... and I fear it.

EditorData.NodeContext: apprehensive

Text.Value: I do not know - but I do know that She allowed me to spare you.
With difficulty - but I can help.
I'm ready. How do I get there?
But then a miracle happened. As I took out my blade, Her voice returned to me... and She told me what I must do to purge myself of doubt.

EditorData.NodeContext: genuine awe of the religious experience

Text.Value: Travel to Moonrise. We will meet again there, at the heart of the Absolute's power.

EditorData.NodeContext: giving orders, friendly tone

Text.Value: To gather our forces in this region. They're ill-disciplined - without a strong hand, they'll disperse.
Where will you go now?
When the Absolute failed to answer me, I feared that you had somehow infected me with that same absence.

EditorData.NodeContext: thoughtful, considering our fate

Text.Value: I asked Her why She had chosen you, made you one of Her faithful, when you are so clearly broken. Beautiful, but broken.

EditorData.NodeContext: thoughtful, considering our fate

EditorData.NodeContext: sad, our fate is decided, and she must kill us

Text.Value: I prefer to decide my own fate.

*In your dream, you stand over yourself as you sleep. A knife in your hand, murder in your heart.*

EditorData.NodeContext: confusion

EditorData.NodeContext: regret

We're both worthy. Let's go to the Absolute together.

Text.Value: It is time - kill her!
It is time! Kill him!
It's time - kill them!

EditorData.NodeContext: Malicious - preparing to kill us

Text.Value: You'd try kill me? I AM THE ABSOLUTE'S FIST!
When you meet Her at Moonrise, She will show you Her design, and your part in it.

The heart of power - what is this Moonrise, exactly?
Don't make this personal. I am a servant of the Absolute, same as you.
*You are ready to strike, to end your own life - but then a shock runs through your mind. This is no dream.*

He was a drow once. Now he is an abomination, a victim of Lolth's cruelty.
The land around Moonrise is cursed. Travelling there will sap your strength and your sanity.

Synopsis: Minthara ambushes a player during the night, standing over them with a knife. This can occur almost immediately after sleeping with her, in which case she regrets what she is about to do, and can be convinced not to go through with it.
